Package: GenomicInteractionHub
Type: Package
Version: 0.99.3
Title: A R/Bioconductor package to detect the interaction hub from
       HiC/HiChIP/HiCAR data
Authors@R: c(person(given="Jianhong", family="Ou", email="jianhong.ou@duke.edu", 
        role=c("aut", "cre")),
        person(given="Yarui", family="Diao", role="fnd"))
Maintainer: Jianhong Ou <jianhong.ou@duke.edu>
Description: The GenomicInteractionHub package can import interactions from bedpe file
        and define the interaction hubs, the genomic interaction sites with
        multiple interaction loops.
        The interaction hub is a binding platform regulates one or multiple genes. 
        The detected interaction hubs will be annotated for downstream validation.
License: file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0), stats
Imports: AnnotationDbi, graph, GO.db, 
        GenomicRanges, GenomicFeatures,
        methods,
        IRanges,
        RBGL,
        S4Vectors
Suggests: RUnit, BiocStyle, knitr, rmarkdown, rtracklayer, testthat,
        TxDb.Hsapiens.UCSC.hg19.knownGene, org.Hs.eg.db
URL: https://github.com/jianhong/GenomicInteractionHub
BugReports: https://github.com/jianhong/GenomicInteractionHub/issues
biocViews: HiC, Sequencing, Software 
VignetteBuilder: knitr
